## Section Alternation

Light → Dark → Light → Dark → Light → Dark → Light

| Section | Background |
|---------|------------|
| Hero | `var(--paper)` |
| Manifesto | `var(--paper)` + `border-top: 1px solid var(--line-light)` |
| Who We Are | `radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 35%, var(--ink-soft) 0%, var(--ink) 65%)` |
| The Problem | `var(--paper)` |
| Case Studies | `radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, var(--ink-soft) 0%, var(--ink) 60%)` |
| System | `var(--paper)` |
| Score | `radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 35%, var(--ink-soft) 0%, var(--ink) 65%)` |
| CTA | `radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, #F6F2E9 0%, var(--paper) 65%)` |
| Footer | `var(--ink)` + `border-top: 1px solid var(--line-dark)` |

Every section boundary gets a 1px hairline: `var(--line-light)` on light, `var(--line-dark)` on dark.

