## Motion System

### Lenis + GSAP (loaded in `components/SiteScripts.tsx`)
- Smooth scroll: Lenis `lerp: 0.1`
- All GSAP animations via `ScrollTrigger`, trigger at `top 85%`
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` — skip all animations if set

### Line-Mask Reveal (headlines)
```tsx
// HTML structure:
<h1 className="hero-headline">
  <span className="line-mask"><span className="line-mask-inner">Word</span></span>
</h1>
// CSS: .line-mask { overflow: hidden } .line-mask-inner { transform: translateY(102%) }
// GSAP: animate .line-mask-inner y → 0, power4.out, 1s, stagger 0.12s
```

### .reveal (scroll sections)
```tsx
// Add className="reveal" to headings, paragraphs, key elements
// CSS: opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px)
// GSAP ScrollTrigger animates to opacity: 1, y: 0, power3.out, 0.9s
```

### Easing Cheatsheet
| Use | Ease |
|-----|------|
| Headline reveals | `power4.out` |
| General reveals | `power3.out` |
| Preloader slide | `power4.inOut` |
| Magnetic snap-back | `elastic.out(1, 0.4)` |
| Parallax / scrub | `none` |

### Magnetic Buttons
Applied to `#hero-cta-btn` and `#cta-main-btn`. Do not add to other elements without adding the GSAP handler in SiteScripts.

