## Hero Composition

- Image: `next/image` src `/hero-object.jpg`, `width=820 height=680 priority`
- Container: `.hero-image-wrap` — `position: absolute; bottom: 0; width: min(62vw, 880px)`
- Blend: `mix-blend-mode: multiply` on the `<img>` — dissolves grey bg into bone
- Tilt wrapper: `.hero-image-tilt` (GSAP rotateX/Y on mousemove ±4°)
- Float: CSS `@keyframes heroFloat` (translateY 0→-18px, 7s infinite)
- Parallax: GSAP ScrollTrigger scrub on `#hero-image-wrap` (y: 0 → -120)
- Headline z-index above image: `.hero-text` z-index 2, `.hero-image-wrap` z-index 1

---

## SVG System Diagram

10 component nodes + center "VALIDEX SCORE" in a radial layout (r=180, cx/cy=300).
Node classes: `.diagram-node` (animates in on scroll), `.diagram-line` (stroke-dashoffset draw).
Do not replace with third-party chart lib — user will supply a custom diagram component separately.

---

## Accessibility

- All `<Image>` tags must have descriptive `alt` text
- `prefers-reduced-motion`: SiteScripts checks at init — skip all GSAP if true, set `opacity: 1; transform: none` on `.reveal` elements
- Nav uses `mix-blend-mode: difference` — ensure link text remains legible on all bg colours
- Focus states: Tailwind default ring is fine; do not remove outline

