## File Structure

```
app/
  globals.css          ← ALL styles. No component-level CSS files.
  layout.tsx           ← Font imports (DM Sans + DM Mono), metadata
  page.tsx             ← Section composition (import order = render order)
  case-studies/[slug]/ ← Editorial detail pages (7 static slugs)
components/
  Preloader.tsx        ← #preloader overlay (animated by SiteScripts)
  Nav.tsx              ← Fixed, mix-blend-mode difference
  Hero.tsx             ← 'use client', next/image, line-mask headline
  Manifesto.tsx        ← Word-by-word reveal
  WhoWeAre.tsx         ← Dark section, two-col body
  TheProblem.tsx       ← 85% stat counter (GSAP), pull quote
  CaseStudies.tsx      ← Card grid (7 cards), .cs-grid-section
  System.tsx           ← SVG radial diagram
  Score.tsx            ← Animated scorecard, bar fills, grade scale-in
  CtaSection.tsx       ← line-mask headline, magnetic CTA
  Footer.tsx           ← Dark, thin bar
  SiteScripts.tsx      ← 'use client', ALL GSAP/Lenis logic
public/
  hero-object.jpg      ← Hero image (replace with hero-reference.jpg when available)
```

