## Don'ts

- No `font-weight: 700` on display headlines — use `500`
- No pure `#000` or `#fff` — use tokens
- No `overflow: hidden` on `.cta-headline` (breaks descender visibility)
- No inline `style={{ fontFamily: '...' }}` — use CSS classes
- No new animation logic in component files — all GSAP lives in `SiteScripts.tsx`
- No horizontal scroll on new sections — use card grids or vertical stacks
- No extra 100vh spacers or empty divs
- No serif fonts anywhere — DM Sans and DM Mono only
- No emojis as UI icons — use SVG or text symbols (→ ↗ ←)
